      "text": [
        " قَضَى أَمِيرُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ ( عليه السلام ) فِي فَرَسَيْنِ اصْطَدَمَا فَمَاتَ أَحَدُهُمَا فَضَمَّنَ الْبَاقِيَ دِيَةَ الْمَيِّتِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ahmad Bin Muhammad Al Kufy, from Ibrahim Bin Al Hassan, from Muhammad Bin Khalaf, from Musa Bin Ibrahim Al Marouzy, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan Musa<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> judged regarding two horses collided, so one of the two dies. So the responsibility is upon the (owner of the) remaining one, wergild of the dead (horse)’."
        ]
